pr_title: handle old cmake with newer llvm
pr_body:
Users might want to use llvm with an older, officially unsupported cmake (see our CI).
In this case we don't want to use the tablegen function from llvm but rather our own replacement which doesn't use the TRANSFORM command.

Will add a test for the remainder in a sec.
